&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/ASIA-SHANGHAI-EL-WILLY-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-7589&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/ASIA-SHANGHAI-EL-WILLY-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;ASIA- SHANGHAI- EL WILLY- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;166&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;With a spectacular view of the Shanghai skyline, El Willy is located on the 5&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; floor of an historic 1906 building at the south end of the Bund. While the d&eacute;cor is industrial and whimsical at the same time, the contemporary Spanish cuisine by Chef Willy Trullas Moreno is serious, earning a place on the World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants Global Selection. He combines traditional Spanish dishes with Chinese yin/yang meal structure and techniques learned from experience working with some of the world&rsquo;s most famed chefs in Spain, France and New York. Dishes such as Willy&rsquo;s Seafood Paella, Scallop Ceviche and Explosive Balik Salmon with sour cream and truffle honey are served family style and are meant to be shared. Stylish casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book by phone at +86-21-5404-5757 or by email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:gary@el-willy.com&quot;&gt;gary@el-willy.com&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or&nbsp;local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The restaurant will call you to reconfirm your reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment must be made with your Diners Club card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

